#### Loss 函数

```python
total = (
    beta_rgb * l_rgb           # RGB reconstruction loss
    + (1 - beta_rgb) * l_depth # Depth reconstruction loss
    + lambda_pose * l_pose     # Pose regularization
    + l_abs_pose               # Absolute pose prior
